org.enterprisedomain.classmaker

Interface ModelBlueprint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface ModelBlueprint
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Model Blueprint'. Input model specification for making.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dynamic Model
    • Dependencies
    • Completion Listener
    • Executor
    See Also:
    org.enterprisedomain.classmaker.ClassMakerPackage#getModelBlueprint()
